.container.student-about.referral
  .row
    .col-xs-12
      div(ncy-breadcrumb)
  .row
    .col-xs-12.section-header
      h3
        | Study with your friends & Earn $25 for each referral.*
      h5
        | Great thing your friend will also earn $25
  .row
    .col-xs-12
      .steps-to-take
        .step
          i.fa.fa-user-plus
          h4.text Invite
        .step
          i.fa.fa-sign-in
          h4.text Sign Up
        .step
          i.fa.fa-money
          h4.text Earn
      .note
        | *Once your referral successfully joins the paid program, you and your friend will receive upto $25 in cash.
      h5 Share message
  .row
    .col-xs-12.col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
